00:53:44.750 --> 00:53:47.640
<i>Every white politician</i>

755
00:53:47.710 --> 00:53:50.793
<i>who feeds on prejudice and hatred.</i>

756
00:53:53.070 --> 00:53:56.711
<i>Every white preacher
who preaches the Bible</i>


757
00:53:56.790 --> 00:53:59.600
<i>and stays silent
