758
00:54:03.830 --> 00:54:06.674
<i>Who murdered Jimmie Lee Jackson?</i>

759
00:54:07.870 --> 00:54:13.752
<i>Every Negro man and woman
who stands by without joining this fight</i>


760
00:54:13.830 --> 00:54:16.754
