00:54:33.830 --> 00:54:36.401
<i>And when I heard just yesterday</i>

765
00:54:36.470 --> 00:54:38.279
<i>that Malcolm X,</i>

766
00:54:38.350 --> 00:54:41.593
<i>who stood in this very church
