767
00:54:41.670 --> 00:54:43.672
<i>had been shot and killed,</i>

768
00:54:45.470 --> 00:54:47.791
<i>I turned to my wife Coretta</i>

769
00:54:47.870 --> 00:54:52.512
<i>and said the same thing I often say
