946
01:06:30.950 --> 01:06:33.351
<i>I just think it'd be a mistake
to hold people back</i>


947
01:06:33.430 --> 01:06:34.955
<i>when their blood is up.</i>

948
01:06:36.390 --> 01:06:40.031
<i>I hear you,
but we need to be out there full throttle.</i>


949
01:06:40.110 --> 01:06:42.681
<i>This ain't a test run.</i>

950
01:06:42.750 --> 01:06:44.195
<i>We need to get to Montgomery.</i>

951
01:06:44.270 --> 01:06:46.841
<i>I warned Johnson that
we were going to the Capitol.</i>


952
01:06:46.910 --> 01:06:48.753
<i>We need to do just that.</i>

953
01:06:49.750 --> 01:06:53.072
<i>And I believe we will. 
We'll get there.</i>

954
01:06:56.910 --> 01:06:59.231
<i>And when we do the real deal,
the finale,</i>


955
01:06:59.310 --> 01:07:01.392
<i>when you make the big speech
at the end,</i>


956
01:07:01.470 --> 01:07:03.711
<i>right on Wallace's doorstep.</i>

957
01:07:18.470 --> 01:07:20.916
<i>I don't know, Andy.</i>

958
01:07:22.230 --> 01:07:24.073
<i>It'll be just fine.</i>

959
01:07:24.630 --> 01:07:28.316
<i>We'll get it started strong.
And you'll finish strong.</i>


960
01:07:34.790 --> 01:07:36.952
Okay. Let's proceed.

961
01:07:37.670 --> 01:07:39.593
<i>But only one of us walks to start.</i>

962
01:07:39.670 --> 01:07:43.641
<i>I don't want to get back on Monday
and find all our leadership in jail.</i>


963
01:07:44.510 --> 01:07:45.750
<i>One of us walks.</i>

964
01:07:46.350 --> 01:07:47.840
<i>Understood.</i>

965
01:07:50.670 --> 01:07:54.834
<i>There will be no march
from Selma to Montgomery.</i>


966
01:07:55.150 --> 01:07:58.757
<i>It is not conducive to traffic flow
on Route 80.</i>


967
01:07:58.830 --> 01:08:00.275
<i>Or to public safety.</i>

968
01:08:00.350 --> 01:08:01.954
Your lives could be in danger,

969
01:08:02.030 --> 01:08:04.237
but we're going to be strong
if we stick together.


970
01:08:04.310 --> 01:08:07.553
Don't fight back.
It's a non-violent movement.


971
01:08:07.990 --> 01:08:11.039
Non-violence is not passive.
It's actually very strong.


972
01:08:11.670 --> 01:08:14.913
We shouldn't do this, John.
This is not us. This is not SNCC.


973
01:08:14.990 --> 01:08:16.230
It's some bullshit.

974
01:08:16.350 --> 01:08:19.559
It's gonna do more for King
and the SCLC than for Selma.


975
01:08:19.950 --> 01:08:21.076
This is Alabama.

976
01:08:21.190 --> 01:08:23.591
They can keep their asses
in Washington, D.C.


977
01:08:23.670 --> 01:08:25.911
You don't tell us
how to live our lives.

978
01:08:25.990 --> 01:08:28.311
This is an example of what
you might deal with out there.


979
01:08:28.390 --> 01:08:31.473
What you might experience.
