980
01:08:31.550 --> 01:08:33.473
We don't want your kind here.

981
01:08:33.550 --> 01:08:35.154
Go to the bottom
of the river, black boy.

982
01:08:35.230 --> 01:08:36.834
<i>We're going to put you down
